(41, 10, 23, 42, 18, 24, 24, 'How hardly shall they that have riches enter into the kingdom of God!', 'Connection on Wealth and Salvation', 'Both passages emphasize the difficulty for those with riches to enter the kingdom of God. The wording in both verses is nearly identical, underscoring a shared teaching of Jesus regarding wealth and spiritual entry.', 'parallel', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
