(41, 10, 24, 19, 62, 10, 10, 'trust in riches', 'Connection on Trust and Riches', 'Both passages emphasize the danger of placing trust in riches. Mark 10:24 warns about the difficulty for those who trust in riches to enter the kingdom of God, while Psalms 62:10 advises against setting one''s heart on increasing wealth.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
